## Phase 10: Demo Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant S as Student
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant AI as AI Agents
    participant RZ as Razorpay
    participant F as Funder

    Note over S,F: 1. REJECTION DEMO (Core Rule 1)
    S->>FE: Enters Rs. 500 amount
    FE-->>S: вќЊ Inline error: "Min Rs. 2,000"
    
    Note over S,F: 2. VALID REQUEST
    S->>FE: Submit Rs. 5,000 exam_fee request
    FE->>BE: POST /requests
    BE->>BE: Validate (amount в‰Ґ 2000 вњ“, category вњ“, freq cap вњ“)
    BE-->>FE: 201 Created

    Note over S,F: 3. VERIFICATION
    BE->>AI: Verification Agent (Tesseract + GPT-4o-mini)
    AI-->>BE: {score: 87, flags: []}

    Note over S,F: 4. URGENCY + MATCHING
    BE->>AI: Urgency Engine в†’ "High"
    BE->>AI: Matching Engine в†’ Top 3 funders

    Note over S,F: 5. FUNDER APPROVAL + PAYMENT
    F->>FE: Views anonymous card, clicks "Approve"
    FE->>BE: POST /disburse/{id}
    BE->>RZ: Create order (Rs. 5,000)
    RZ-->>FE: Checkout modal
    F->>RZ: Test card payment
    RZ-->>BE: Webhook: payment success

    Note over S,F: 6. IMPACT REPORT
    BE->>AI: Impact Agent в†’ Generate PDF
    BE-->>F: Download link
```

